&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;At Jungle Scout, we are on a mission to build the best Amazon competitive intelligence tools for Amazon sellers and brands.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a detail-oriented and dependable Accounts Payable &amp;amp; Cash Specialist to join our finance team on a &lt;strong&gt;part-time basis&lt;/strong&gt;. This is a hands-on role at the core of our financial operations — responsible for keeping vendor relationships running smoothly, cash activity accurate, and our books clean.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll work closely with a collaborative accounting team and have real ownership over the day-to-day processes that keep our business moving. If you take pride in precision, thrive in a structured environment, and enjoy building systems that just work, this role is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own Accounts Payable&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review, code, and process vendor invoices accurately and on time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Code and sync expenses from Ramp to our GL system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and execute weekly payment runs (checks, ACH, wire transfers)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain vendor records and resolve discrepancies or billing issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to vendor inquiries professionally and promptly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manage Cash Activity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Record daily cash transactions and reconcile bank accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor cash balances and support cash flow tracking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare bank deposits and maintain thorough supporting documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with month-end close activities related to cash and payables&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Support the Broader Finance Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate, well-organized financial records&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with audits by preparing and providing requested documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to process improvements and internal controls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate on ad hoc projects as the team&#39;s needs evolve&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Success Looks Like&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Invoices processed accurately and payment runs executed without errors or delays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bank accounts reconciled consistently and on schedule&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vendor relationships maintained with professionalism and responsiveness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Month-end close supported with clean, reliable documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Processes that are tighter and more efficient over time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of experience in accounts payable, bookkeeping, or a similar finance role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid understanding of core accounting principles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experienced with accounting software such as Sage Intacct, NetSuite, or similar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable in Microsoft Excel — data entry, basic formulas, and reconciliations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptionally detail-oriented with strong organizational habits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-directed and reliable — you manage your time well and meet your deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bonus: experience with cash management or treasury functions, ERP systems, or a SaaS/technology environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em data-stringify-type=&quot;italic&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note: &lt;/strong&gt;The one constant in our evolving, dynamic environment is change. Needless to say, you’ll never get bored ;) &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em data-stringify-type=&quot;italic&quot;&gt;The responsibilities listed above

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;At Jungle Scout, we are on a mission to build the best Amazon competitive intelligence tools for Amazon sellers and brands.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Scientist&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Full-Time Remote | Brazil&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Jungle Scout&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;We&#39;re on a mission to build the best Amazon competitive intelligence tools for sellers and brands worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;We&#39;re looking for a Data Scientist to join our team and help leverage large-scale data to drive growth for businesses on Amazon. You&#39;ll develop new data science areas of our product from conception through to scaling in production, working closely with our engineering team to apply expertise in data analysis and machine learning to create solutions that deliver actionable insights to our customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll have the ability to influence the direction of the product while working on an area that&#39;s at the core of our business — one our customers depend on to run their own businesses successfully. You&#39;ll also be supported by a dedicated team of ML Engineering/Ops experts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build real-time machine learning models utilizing very large datasets to deliver scalable solutions to customer problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with product managers, engineers, and designers to build and iterate on data-driven features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive data exploration and experimentation to identify new product opportunities using Amazon and e-commerce behavioral data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and run experiments to evaluate the impact of optimizations and communicate results to stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish scalable, efficient, and automated processes for large-scale data analysis, model development, and inference&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build scalable pipelines using Python, SQL, and AWS to operationalize insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define metrics, create dashboards, and monitor model performance in production&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion best practices in model development, testing, and monitoring&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write production-ready code&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Must-Have&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience conceptualizing, building, and deploying algorithms and models to production alongside machine learning engineers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong machine learning best practices with a solid statistical background&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical proficiency in Python&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with deep learning frameworks such as TensorFlow and PyTorch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong command of SQL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience translating customer needs into data problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience presenting clear analysis and conclusions to a wide variety of stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep curiosity about data and the Amazon domain&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort dealing with ambiguity, making tradeoffs, and adjusting plans as you learn&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in the software development lifecycle using version control, CI/CD, and multiple environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nice-to-Have&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Spark, SageMaker, S3&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with other AWS services like EC2, CloudWatch, Athena, Postgres, Docker&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Jupyter notebooks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
